WEBVTT

00:00:08.510 --> 00:00:10.370
Jaehun agreed to let you come out?

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:14.500
Soohyung.

00:00:18.380 --> 00:00:20.380
Do you know what's the relationship

00:00:21.550 --> 00:00:23.120
between Jaehun and Minwoo?

00:00:28.010 --> 00:00:28.460
Why?

00:00:29.560 --> 00:00:31.240
Why don't you just ask him?

00:00:36.340 --> 00:00:39.260
Are you afraid of
you'd hear an answer you don't want to,

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:39.830
or

00:00:41.140 --> 00:00:42.870
do you not believe what he says?

00:00:46.330 --> 00:00:47.350
I asked Jaehun.

00:00:50.250 --> 00:00:52.080
He said there's nothing between them.

00:00:52.080 --> 00:00:52.620
But...

00:00:55.570 --> 00:00:57.830
Do friends act like that with each other?

00:00:59.950 --> 00:01:00.550
Well...

00:01:01.230 --> 00:01:03.910
There are many kinds of friendships.

00:01:06.020 --> 00:01:08.250
Some friends just have fun together.

00:01:09.470 --> 00:01:11.720
Some friends lick each other's wounds.

00:01:12.630 --> 00:01:15.960
Some friends are pure and honest,
with no ulterior motives.

00:01:16.460 --> 00:01:18.890
And some friends let their guard down
in times of need

00:01:18.890 --> 00:01:20.820
and keep each other's bodies warm.

00:01:23.450 --> 00:01:26.190
The three of us are childhood friends,

00:01:27.820 --> 00:01:29.820
but as for their relationship,

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:32.750
isn't it better to ask them directly?

00:01:49.700 --> 00:01:51.430
Didn't you say you don't drink?

00:01:57.340 --> 00:01:58.360
Soohyung.

00:02:00.390 --> 00:02:03.320
What do you think about
my relationship with Jaehun?

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.390
Jaehun said...

00:02:09.220 --> 00:02:10.400
he loved me.

00:02:10.620 --> 00:02:11.250
But...

00:02:14.790 --> 00:02:16.290
What is love?

00:02:18.760 --> 00:02:20.880
Is such oppression love?

00:02:23.530 --> 00:02:25.100
I don't understand him.

00:02:29.870 --> 00:02:31.130
Right now,

00:02:33.530 --> 00:02:34.590
he's in a stable mood,

00:02:34.590 --> 00:02:36.040
and I'm obedient

00:02:36.040 --> 00:02:37.070
and cheerful,

00:02:38.900 --> 00:02:40.440
so he likes me.

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:41.440
But...

00:02:45.470 --> 00:02:47.470
what if I'm no longer cheerful?

00:02:51.550 --> 00:02:53.620
Then, will he still love me back?

00:02:56.350 --> 00:02:57.770
In my opinion,

00:02:58.690 --> 00:02:59.950
Han Jaehun

00:03:00.420 --> 00:03:02.070
is serious about you.

00:03:19.590 --> 00:03:20.820
This drug is mild,

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:23.450
and basically has no side effects.

00:03:24.130 --> 00:03:25.800
It relaxes you,

00:03:26.300 --> 00:03:27.960
and makes you drop your guard.

00:03:29.850 --> 00:03:31.180
It empties your mind

00:03:32.340 --> 00:03:34.340
and heightens sensory perception.

00:03:35.750 --> 00:03:37.420
You can put it in wine or water.

00:03:38.030 --> 00:03:40.360
It's basically colorless and tasteless.

00:03:40.820 --> 00:03:41.600
Maybe

00:03:42.190 --> 00:03:44.790
this is a surefire way
to resolve your queries.

00:03:47.390 --> 00:03:49.990
Of course, whether you use it or not
is up to you.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:53.200
I'm just providing you with a suggestion.

00:03:54.130 --> 00:03:54.980
However,

00:03:55.800 --> 00:03:58.300
living in constant suspicion and anxiety

00:03:58.900 --> 00:04:00.150
is too agonizing,

00:04:01.260 --> 00:04:02.070
isn't it?

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:07.460
I've paid the bill.

00:04:08.570 --> 00:04:10.370
Take your time to think about it.

00:04:11.030 --> 00:04:12.290
Shall I call you a taxi?

00:04:14.370 --> 00:04:15.250
I'm good.

00:04:17.630 --> 00:04:18.620
Bye then.

00:04:57.810 --> 00:04:59.140
Goodness, what is this?

00:05:01.330 --> 00:05:02.440
Jaehun.

00:05:02.990 --> 00:05:03.690
Hi.

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:06.020
Haejun.

00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:07.480
What's wrong?

00:05:18.310 --> 00:05:18.960
Haejun.

00:05:19.870 --> 00:05:21.270
Why did you drink so much?

00:05:22.460 --> 00:05:23.190
Jaehun.

00:05:24.300 --> 00:05:24.870
Jaehun.

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:27.390
Do you love me?

00:05:30.350 --> 00:05:31.670
You can't answer...

00:05:32.690 --> 00:05:34.090
I guess you don't love me.

00:05:37.590 --> 00:05:38.540
You're drunk.

00:05:39.659 --> 00:05:41.120
Let's talk about it later.

00:05:42.570 --> 00:05:43.909
When is "later"?

00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:48.220
You say you love me,

00:05:48.220 --> 00:05:50.350
so how can you do that with Yoon Minwoo?

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:54.480
How many times must I tell you

00:05:54.680 --> 00:05:56.940
that there's nothing between him and me?

00:05:58.430 --> 00:06:00.530
You said that before, but...

00:06:01.960 --> 00:06:04.110
That's what you always say to me.

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:06.250
OK, OK.

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:11.010
How much do you love me?

00:06:11.420 --> 00:06:12.290
Yes, I love you.

00:06:12.290 --> 00:06:14.150
Do you love me to the moon and back?

00:06:21.960 --> 00:06:23.390
I really love you.

00:06:23.390 --> 00:06:24.160
OK.

00:06:24.340 --> 00:06:25.990
I love you.

00:06:31.090 --> 00:06:32.890
What did you eat while drinking?

00:06:33.380 --> 00:06:34.590
Nothing.

00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:36.880
Then why are you so heavy?

00:06:37.180 --> 00:06:38.530
I really didn't.

00:06:38.900 --> 00:06:40.220
Goodness, don't lie.

00:06:40.830 --> 00:06:41.960
I really didn't eat.

00:06:42.290 --> 00:06:43.280
Eat less supper.

00:06:43.500 --> 00:06:45.020
I said I didn't eat much.

00:06:56.770 --> 00:06:58.140
Jaehun.

00:06:59.110 --> 00:07:00.110
Where are you?

00:07:00.550 --> 00:07:02.000
I'm here.

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:13.480
Jaehun.

00:07:15.200 --> 00:07:16.050
Haejun.

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:19.360
Who did you drink with to get this drunk?

00:07:20.270 --> 00:07:21.500
Jaehun!

00:07:22.670 --> 00:07:24.380
Do you really love me?

00:07:31.310 --> 00:07:32.810
Of course.

00:07:33.130 --> 00:07:34.310
My Haejun.

00:07:40.810 --> 00:07:43.140
I'm not saying this because you're drunk.

00:07:44.730 --> 00:07:46.210
Even if you forget

00:07:47.550 --> 00:07:49.480
and ask me again tomorrow morning,

00:07:50.510 --> 00:07:52.310
my answer will still be the same.

00:07:54.030 --> 00:07:56.430
I'm not saying this
because of our contract

00:07:56.990 --> 00:07:58.909
or because

00:07:59.250 --> 00:08:00.580
you're younger than me.

00:08:02.630 --> 00:08:03.530
I love you

00:08:06.500 --> 00:08:08.300
because you're you, Kim Haejun.

00:08:09.570 --> 00:08:11.050
Then...

00:08:12.770 --> 00:08:13.880
prove it to me.

00:09:19.980 --> 00:09:20.830
You're awake.

00:09:24.840 --> 00:09:26.560
My head hurts.

00:09:27.480 --> 00:09:29.880
I don't remember
what happened last night.

00:09:35.090 --> 00:09:36.120
Well,

00:09:37.340 --> 00:09:39.110
how about I jog your memory?

00:09:43.160 --> 00:09:44.340
No need.

00:09:47.940 --> 00:09:49.940
You were drunk last night.

00:09:50.450 --> 00:09:55.080
You kept asking me if I love you or not.

00:09:55.800 --> 00:09:57.930
There's more. I'll help you recall it.

00:09:59.270 --> 00:10:00.870
No, no.

00:10:01.880 --> 00:10:03.880
It's OK. You can stop here.

00:10:24.330 --> 00:10:25.800
Stop teasing me!

00:10:31.310 --> 00:10:32.380
Put this first,

00:10:32.380 --> 00:10:34.380
then add butter and mix it together.

00:10:34.920 --> 00:10:35.900
And water...

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:36.950
It's so hard.

00:10:40.570 --> 00:10:43.300
Do you have to study recipes
to make some cookies?

00:10:43.590 --> 00:10:44.420
Of course.

00:10:44.850 --> 00:10:46.850
You've always been baking by feel.

00:10:48.970 --> 00:10:49.850
Look.

00:10:50.210 --> 00:10:51.110
With butter,

00:10:51.110 --> 00:10:53.110
its softness is crucial.

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:55.360
When you press it with your fingers,

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:56.960
it should make a slight dent.

00:10:57.360 --> 00:11:00.430
If the ratio of sugar to flour
is even slightly different,

00:11:00.430 --> 00:11:02.490
the taste will be totally different.

00:11:02.900 --> 00:11:05.150
It's my first time
baking gingerbread cookies.

00:11:05.150 --> 00:11:07.010
Of course I have to do it properly.

00:11:09.950 --> 00:11:11.090
What if I say

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:14.960
I'll make it by feel,

00:11:16.530 --> 00:11:17.890
will you trust me

00:11:18.470 --> 00:11:19.820
or the recipe more?

00:11:21.010 --> 00:11:21.730
Then,

00:11:22.290 --> 00:11:23.340
let's make a bet.

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:24.920
A bet?

00:11:26.660 --> 00:11:29.590
I'll make it according to the recipe,
and you by feel.

00:11:30.520 --> 00:11:32.520
Let's see whose cookies are better.

00:11:33.180 --> 00:11:34.840
The appearance is important,

00:11:34.870 --> 00:11:36.870
but the taste is the most important.

00:11:38.420 --> 00:11:39.360
Then,

00:11:39.800 --> 00:11:41.130
what's the punishment?

00:11:42.480 --> 00:11:44.680
How about the loser agrees to a request?

00:11:45.590 --> 00:11:47.250
Nothing too unreasonable...

00:11:47.740 --> 00:11:48.870
Acting like a puppy?

00:11:50.750 --> 00:11:51.200
Sure.

00:11:51.810 --> 00:11:53.210
Deal. Let's go with that.

00:11:53.220 --> 00:11:53.760
OK.

00:11:54.860 --> 00:11:56.360
Don't peek at my recipe.

00:11:57.880 --> 00:11:59.500
I don't need to, OK?

00:12:00.900 --> 00:12:02.910
Turn around. I'll tie your apron for you.

00:12:02.910 --> 00:12:03.360
OK.

00:12:06.260 --> 00:12:06.720
My hand!

00:12:08.010 --> 00:12:08.470
My hand.

00:12:25.840 --> 00:12:26.440
Is it done?

00:12:27.380 --> 00:12:28.180
You look good.

00:12:29.540 --> 00:12:29.950
I know.

00:12:30.380 --> 00:12:31.000
You know?

00:12:32.690 --> 00:12:33.680
You can start first.

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:34.750
OK, I'll start.

00:12:35.480 --> 00:12:36.200
No peeking.

00:12:36.300 --> 00:12:36.750
OK.

00:12:40.230 --> 00:12:41.490
You shouldn't do that.

00:12:42.050 --> 00:12:43.370
I'm doing just fine.

00:12:43.980 --> 00:12:45.210
Don't peek!

00:12:47.180 --> 00:12:48.350
Good luck then.

00:12:52.090 --> 00:12:53.820
Can you pass me a cookie cutter?

00:12:57.070 --> 00:12:58.130
Hurry up and start.

00:13:09.800 --> 00:13:10.860
Jaehun, look at me.

00:13:13.630 --> 00:13:14.160
Argh, no.

00:13:14.340 --> 00:13:14.990
Just once!

00:13:15.160 --> 00:13:16.330
No, a little later.

00:13:16.400 --> 00:13:17.230
A little later?

00:13:17.230 --> 00:13:17.850
Yeah.

00:13:18.220 --> 00:13:19.430
I need to make my cookies.

00:13:19.430 --> 00:13:19.840
Ah.

00:13:20.050 --> 00:13:20.920
A little later?

00:13:25.630 --> 00:13:26.090
Jaehun.

00:13:26.160 --> 00:13:26.570
Hmm?

00:13:26.950 --> 00:13:27.550
Come here.

00:13:28.270 --> 00:13:28.820
Why?

00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:30.600
I have something to tell you.

00:13:31.970 --> 00:13:32.520
What is it?

00:13:32.520 --> 00:13:33.450
Close your eyes.

00:13:35.440 --> 00:13:36.520
Don't do anything weird.

00:13:36.520 --> 00:13:37.320
I won't.

00:13:42.870 --> 00:13:43.530
Don't move.

00:13:43.720 --> 00:13:44.330
Don't do it!

00:13:44.330 --> 00:13:45.260
Don't move!

00:13:56.480 --> 00:13:57.820
You're a kitty cat now.

00:13:58.580 --> 00:13:59.310
Seriously?

00:13:59.700 --> 00:14:00.410
Seriously?

00:14:00.780 --> 00:14:01.710
Aren't you bold?

00:14:02.630 --> 00:14:03.240
Come here.

00:14:05.250 --> 00:14:06.310
No, I don't want to.

00:14:07.190 --> 00:14:08.190
I'll make it cute.

00:14:08.910 --> 00:14:09.510
Very cute.

00:14:10.070 --> 00:14:10.670
Do it then.

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:14.370
What is this? Am I crying?

00:14:14.800 --> 00:14:15.930
I'll put more on you.

00:14:16.180 --> 00:14:16.910
No, no.

00:14:17.190 --> 00:14:17.630
Your nose.

00:14:17.630 --> 00:14:18.690
You need a cat nose.

00:14:19.110 --> 00:14:20.270
OK, then...

00:14:20.780 --> 00:14:21.440
Right here.

00:14:22.200 --> 00:14:23.260
That isn't my nose.

00:14:23.930 --> 00:14:24.990
What are you doing?

00:14:29.130 --> 00:14:30.220
You look so silly.

00:14:32.130 --> 00:14:33.460
Where are you aiming at?

00:14:36.180 --> 00:14:37.110
Looking good.

00:14:37.860 --> 00:14:38.940
Come here.

00:14:47.100 --> 00:14:47.750
Are you done?

00:14:47.750 --> 00:14:48.280
Yeah.

00:14:48.930 --> 00:14:49.890
I want to do some more.

00:14:49.890 --> 00:14:50.650
Don't.

00:14:50.650 --> 00:14:51.670
Don't.

00:14:52.900 --> 00:14:53.800
Calm down.

00:14:54.100 --> 00:14:55.010
Calm down?

00:14:59.620 --> 00:15:00.250
It's done!

00:15:03.110 --> 00:15:04.110
It's so hot.

00:15:10.340 --> 00:15:10.960
Come here.

00:15:14.760 --> 00:15:15.290
Strange.

00:15:16.280 --> 00:15:18.150
Why do yours look nicer than mine?

00:15:20.690 --> 00:15:21.550
Let's taste it.

00:15:21.920 --> 00:15:22.250
OK.

00:15:22.680 --> 00:15:23.820
Open your mouth.

00:15:24.260 --> 00:15:24.860
Oh, right,

00:15:25.470 --> 00:15:27.870
my teacher, Mr. Kang,
will be here tomorrow.

00:15:27.870 --> 00:15:29.470
Should we leave some for him?

00:15:32.790 --> 00:15:34.120
Your teacher, Mr. Kang?

00:15:34.420 --> 00:15:35.010
Yeah.

00:15:36.700 --> 00:15:38.020
When did he become

00:15:38.870 --> 00:15:40.330
Mr. Kang?

00:15:40.440 --> 00:15:41.100
Well,

00:15:41.870 --> 00:15:43.470
he gives me drawing lessons.

00:15:43.870 --> 00:15:46.930
It's the end of the year.
It's nice to hang out together.

00:15:47.860 --> 00:15:49.260
Fine, have your lessons.

00:15:49.440 --> 00:15:50.180
Are you mad?

00:15:51.410 --> 00:15:52.310
Look at me.

00:15:58.030 --> 00:15:59.050
You're so sly,

00:15:59.290 --> 00:15:59.940
huh?

00:16:00.570 --> 00:16:01.570
Are you still mad?

00:16:05.120 --> 00:16:06.120
Try the cookies.

00:16:19.160 --> 00:16:20.410
Draw this like this.

00:16:45.400 --> 00:16:46.820
Mr. Kang.

00:16:59.720 --> 00:17:01.310
Mr. Kang.

00:17:06.040 --> 00:17:08.040
Do you have to stand there and watch?

00:17:15.400 --> 00:17:16.500
I can't stand you.

00:17:20.690 --> 00:17:23.890
This is my house.
It's none of your business where I stand.

00:17:24.970 --> 00:17:25.599
What?

00:17:26.619 --> 00:17:28.369
Am I interrupting your lesson?

00:17:29.500 --> 00:17:31.230
Aren't you a professional?

00:17:32.600 --> 00:17:33.930
Is this the time to joke?

00:17:54.870 --> 00:17:55.570
Soohyung.

00:17:55.570 --> 00:17:56.070
Yeah?

00:17:56.600 --> 00:17:57.850
Have dinner with us.

00:18:00.520 --> 00:18:01.250
Should I?

00:18:02.600 --> 00:18:03.530
Why? It'd be nice.

00:18:03.530 --> 00:18:04.750
You're free anyway.

00:18:07.390 --> 00:18:08.210
Right.

00:18:08.660 --> 00:18:10.260
It's late. Eat before you go.

00:18:20.710 --> 00:18:21.380
Haejun.

00:18:22.460 --> 00:18:24.590
Why do you want to have dinner with him?

00:18:25.100 --> 00:18:26.650
Because it's Christmas.

00:18:26.960 --> 00:18:28.620
It's lively with more people.

00:18:29.230 --> 00:18:30.230
But I

00:18:32.180 --> 00:18:33.980
want to just spend time with you.

00:19:01.520 --> 00:19:02.610
Are you crazy?

00:19:03.170 --> 00:19:04.430
Soohyung is watching.

00:19:06.740 --> 00:19:07.690
He can't see us.

00:19:44.320 --> 00:19:45.650
Darn you.

00:19:45.990 --> 00:19:47.650
You're doing this on purpose.

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:23.990
Hey, Kim.

00:20:30.580 --> 00:20:31.540
It looks like

00:20:32.860 --> 00:20:34.060
Jaehun's heart is set

00:20:34.780 --> 00:20:36.380
and there's no turning back.

00:20:39.550 --> 00:20:41.260
I've done everything I could.

00:20:42.560 --> 00:20:43.530
But

00:20:44.570 --> 00:20:46.170
in the end, people do change.

00:20:51.200 --> 00:20:52.130
I've got a call.

00:20:52.620 --> 00:20:53.480
I'm hanging up.

00:21:01.330 --> 00:21:02.480
Hey, Minwoo.

00:21:03.630 --> 00:21:04.730
I'm leaving.

00:21:06.540 --> 00:21:07.470
You're leaving?

00:21:07.930 --> 00:21:09.480
You came back not long ago.

00:21:10.420 --> 00:21:12.220
Not spending Christmas with us?

00:21:12.650 --> 00:21:14.250
There's nothing I want here.

00:21:15.660 --> 00:21:17.990
I thought I could
have fun with Han Jaehun,

00:21:18.140 --> 00:21:19.740
but he's become more boring.

00:21:21.950 --> 00:21:24.590
I thought he'd be stuck in his own ways,

00:21:25.870 --> 00:21:28.400
so it'd be fun to throw him a problem

00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:29.640
every now and then

00:21:29.640 --> 00:21:31.300
and see how it shake things up.

00:21:33.030 --> 00:21:34.610
To see him struggle.

00:21:36.510 --> 00:21:37.560
But I was wrong.

00:21:40.530 --> 00:21:41.930
He didn't become boring.

00:21:42.620 --> 00:21:43.880
He's found stability.

00:21:45.450 --> 00:21:47.380
He's started living a normal life,

00:21:47.740 --> 00:21:49.400
learning how to love someone.

00:21:51.000 --> 00:21:53.800
They're emotions,
cheesy and annoying emotions,

00:21:54.640 --> 00:21:56.640
that he never felt in the past.

00:21:58.610 --> 00:22:00.870
But it's enough to watch it once or twice.

00:22:01.100 --> 00:22:02.780
It got boring after a while.

00:22:04.720 --> 00:22:05.590
Don't tell me

00:22:06.110 --> 00:22:07.480
you've fallen for him?

00:22:09.940 --> 00:22:11.550
What are you talking about?

00:22:12.760 --> 00:22:14.060
I'm not like you.

00:22:17.150 --> 00:22:18.650
To be specific,

